<div class="mainBlock">
	
	<div class="notes"><label>Notes</label><br /><%= textilize @person.notes %></div>
<p>
  <b>Name:</b>
  <%=h @person.display_name %>
</p>

<p>
  <b>Email:</b>
  <%=h @person.email %>
</p>

<p>
<b>Groups:</b> 
<% for group in @person.groups %>
<%= group.name%><%="," if group != @person.groups.last %>
<%- end %>
</p>


<%= link_to 'Edit', edit_admin_person_path(@person) %> |
<%= link_to 'Back', admin_people_path %>
</div>


<div class="mainBlock">

This person has the following items:
<ul>
<% @person.items.each do |item| %>
<li><%= item.ident_n_name %> <%= link_to image_tag('icons/left_arrow_icon.gif',:size=>'19x9'), admin_equipment_url(item)%></li>
<% end %>
</ul>
<hr />
At one time it did have these:
<ul>
<% @person.recived_transfers.each do |transfer| %>
<% if not transfer.active? %>
<li><%= transfer.equipment.ident_n_name %> <%=transfer.created_at%></li>
<% end %>
<% end %>
</ul>
</div>